Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:22.75,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when I gave up trying to get out of this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.60,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:41.16,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:46.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I will write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:40.82,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.83,MainF,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, is it okay for you to get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.24,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,I feel good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.53,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:50.33,MainF,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.34,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,I had always wanted to appear in this director's movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:03:00.58,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,My dream came true, even if it was just for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.97,MainF,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.85,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,I hope your dream comes true too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:06.67,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not a great one,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.91,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,as long as it's a dream that you desire from the bottom of your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.25,MainF,Kyosuke's mom,0000,0000,0000,,a dream that you've had for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.19,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.67,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've already found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:37.59,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is it interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:44.14,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Did I disturb you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.96,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.18,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Your form was really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:50.00,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.60,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.72,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The way you shot it is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.84,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You only shot my face and didn't get any of my form at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.61,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's not what I was aiming for...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:07.20,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you shoot without my permission, I'll use my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.40,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,This is why the sports club...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.04,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is pointing at eleven?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei didn't come to wake me up today, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.58,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.58,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Tokimeki," which means "Excitement."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.53,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, can I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're Renji-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're here early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:53.76,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, about what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nah, I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of trying to write the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:13.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But my memory only lasts thirteen hours right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.02,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for me to do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.43,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it a try... together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:28.87,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Besides... you're responsible for it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:29.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:37.67,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You hugged me, confessed to me, and kissed me yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:41.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh, erm, I didn't kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:43.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You did other things, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.09,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it was inevitable in that situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That means you took advantage of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:50.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.68,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, did you write that down in your diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.93,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream I gave up on a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:04.29,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You reminded me of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.80,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.27,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.31,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... Shindou Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.87,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.48,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to take long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.44,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.91,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.45,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.95,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.74,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you have something to say, you can come along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.95,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something you have to say even if it means you're skipping school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.87,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, where should we work on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confirming what time I had my meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:16.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I had my breakfast at seven this morning. It's about time to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:23.21,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see. We could eat something I make at home, but maybe we should just go somewhere to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come with me, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:25.86,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:35.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Wh-Why am I cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:38.97,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say "something I make at home" just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:39.78,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:40.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:44.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, you actually have a good memory, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:47.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If it's within thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.32,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, oh my, oh my. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Shindou Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:56.76,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,How polite of you. I'm Asou Sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.64,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Renji-kun's... elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.64,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:08.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't really want to believe it either, she's my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.72,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,This is my neighbor, Kuze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:21.06,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. I'm a good young man with a sparkling smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.18,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.00,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.61,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:32.63,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your relationship with Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:37.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you're asking about our relationship, I think we're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.74,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Friendships doesn't exist between men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:43.09,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, is that really the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:46.20,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's mostly the guy who ends up with his love unrequited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:50.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, I don't think Renji-kun is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.88,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's just kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.65,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.18,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.01,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly which part of Renji do you think is good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:00.14,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,That child looks silly even from a parent's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:05.46,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Or does he bring out your maternal instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.23,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:13.24,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad because I was worried about not hearing anything of his love life until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.73,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I find it amusing to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:19.68,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,So, which part of Renji did you fall in love with?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.85,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Enough is enough. You're bothering Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:26.61,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,My, that's not true. Right, Chihiro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.11,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You came along with me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.43,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the one who talked to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.09,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You seem serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.43,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aiming to take the perfect attendance award?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.45,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.75,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Then what does matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.48,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:53.25,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important time for Hirono-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:57.02,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,His academic results are at a critical point and full of failing marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:10:00.75,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,His attendance record is poor too, and there's even the possibility that he'll have to repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.66,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,But, even now, he can still save the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.75,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,If he studies and comes to classes regularly, he can become a third-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.87,bw,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,If he studies and comes to classes regularly, he can become a third-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:11.52,bw,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't lure Hirono-senpai into skipping school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.28,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lose-lose situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:19.37,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to throw away your perfect attendance award to talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:23.31,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd hear something more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:28.13,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an issue of interesting or boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:31.63,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,This is about Onii-ch— Hirono-senpai's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:36.42,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,But shouldn't Hirono-kun think about that himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:44.11,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Only Hirono-kun can decide what he's going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.43,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless for outsiders to worry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.85,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Outsiders... no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.86,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Or can you handle the responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:56.61,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Will his future be assured as long as he goes to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.78,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:01.84,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If Hirono-kun refrains from doing what he wants and devotes himself to studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,can he become a successful manga artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.40,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun is mature,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:14.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so wouldn't he have thought about skipping school, drawing manga, studying, and all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:14.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:20.03,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,But Onii-chan is still a student. Right now he should study...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:24.93,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Is the world of manga artists so easy that you can come and go whenever you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing his best to draw, while enduring the pain in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:32.99,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If that comes to nothing, can you handle the responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,And, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:39.40,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're showing your honesty in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:45.19,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you remain unaware of it, you might end up hating yourself one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:50.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you go back now, you might still be in time for the sixth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.67,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.98,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd be good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's my only redeeming quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, are you even writing down what you ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:14.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, since there's a possibility for the nutrition to be biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.61,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Today's lunch was a rare ten points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ten points?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.63,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, today's breakfast was four points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.89,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's dinner was seven points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.87,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a point system?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:30.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Since the number of meals is big, and it's tough to evaluate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:33.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just use a simple point system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.52,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that scary for the person who made the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.55,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Can you cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:44.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can, but the finished product should not be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:48.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my family and cooking don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This book has my ideas for the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.74,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please read it after I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:08.99,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like someone reading what I wrote in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.24,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm borrowing this then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.00,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kinds of things are hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.96,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hard for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.62,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Things you can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:23.59,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be a good idea for me to remember, so I can confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.13,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's like being an editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:32.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The obstacle is that I can't finish writing in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Time is the problem after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:37.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I forget memories and details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:43.78,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The story, setting, and even my impression of the characters change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:48.99,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Many times, I've failed halfway through writing and ended up redoing the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:54.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it seems I tried 31 times in four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:59.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,31 times, eh? It'll be my job to challenge that number, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:03.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:06.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Is there anything else I should pay attention to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:07.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:08.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.97,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Tell me everything that's on your mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.48,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, there was a question in my math class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.94,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,A stake is driven in a field, and a sheep is tied to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:24.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The sheep keeps munching the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What is the area of the resulting circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:31.09,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The square of the length of the string times pi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:34.97,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the sheep even eats the roots of the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:39.43,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The grass can't grow back, and the plain turns into a desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:47.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard this question, I saw an image of that tied sheep slowly starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.97,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,For this novel, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:59.87,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I misunderstood. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.09,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget what I said just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? I won't write it down in my diary then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.86,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You keep a diary too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:21.96,MainF,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're showing your honesty in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:25.55,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you didn't say it... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.10,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.73,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sketching. It's practice for drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.29,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you draw manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:49.44,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Manga, eh. You can't draw a manga if you don't have a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:53.89,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Story? Should I try to think of one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.97,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.79,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I like to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.29,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:05.53,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I just bought this month's issue. Let's read it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:09.80,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The protagonist will definitely... and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:18.14,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan. Shiori or Shimiko, which one do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.51,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.06,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.66,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:27.50,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, please don't read it yet. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.11,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what's wrong about that? Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.11,MainF2,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.01,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:37.17,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I made a promise to Chihiro that we would draw manga together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:41.33,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro has something to do today, so... please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:46.38,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan. Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.79,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.97,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(490,1616,\1c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.51,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because I... stole a march on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:30.46,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to tell him my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.21,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making excuses for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:38.83,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You have always been treading the same ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:45.44,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You want someone to grab your hand and take you somewhere one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.80,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:54.06,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is this Kei? I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something we can discuss on the phone. Can we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.94,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.60,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Come over and play again anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.59,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.38,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.40,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.83,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.08,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm Himura's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.65,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,So I know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.52,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.52,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. I'll teach you a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.51,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,A song?
