Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:44.71,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Iku yamakawa koesari yukaba sabishisa no, hatenamu kuni zo kyou mo tabi yuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.42,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's written by Wakayama Bokusui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.12,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:55.73,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,"How many mountains and rivers must I cross to reach the country where there's no loneliness?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:19:01.64,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though I know no such country actually exists, I too set out on a new journey today."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:06.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cheerful song, even though it mentions loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.38,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I learned this song from Himura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:13.48,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he learned it by heart a long time ago for someone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.60,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:19.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.54,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.62,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry I asked you over so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.92,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, did someone come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.92,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, yeah. Anyway, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.76,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yo. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.26,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're the one this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:43.02,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsumi Kyosuke. You know him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the same class as me, and he's a member of the film research club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:49.09,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm an ex-member of the film research club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.65,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's got something to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.27,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.52,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.52,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.11,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Heh?!
