Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:03.62,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is the only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:06.21,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is the only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.12,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the god of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.12,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She found herself on an island when she began to understand things around her."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:17.47,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The island was small, and one could go around it in half a day by foot."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:20.75,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"All she could see at the beach the ocean, the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:25.14,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,clouds and the horizon stretching as far as she could see in a 360-degree view."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.14,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"There was a mansion on the island."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:32.66,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"There were a huge amount of preserved foods and daily necessities inside the warehouse of the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.15,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,so she did not have to starve."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:39.15,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"There were tons of books which she couldn't finish reading, even if she spent her whole life."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.65,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"They contained everything in this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:47.69,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The stories written in the books were all about people."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.90,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"People cannot live alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.92,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"There were many books with that written in them."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:57.21,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"However, the girl was alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.07,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She lived by herself."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:05.43,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Laughing, crying, things that were previously of value, none of them were needed."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:12.22,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"They were finished. They were completed."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:18.74,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl was the first 'average' person in human history."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:25.46,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"The average of the statistics is exactly the same as the sum of herself."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:30.95,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"That's why everything she does is correct."
